        {
            "title": "港股開市︱初段靠穩 恒指微升3點報23644點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股開市初段靠穩，恒生指數開市報23644點，升3點或0.02%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數開報5374點，跌7點或0.14%；國企指數以8579點開市，跌13點或0.16%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股12.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股12.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">騰訊(00700)昨天收市後派發首季業績，略勝市場預期，其ADR昨晚逆市造好；該股今早開報531.5元，升10.5元或2.02%。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240509_FI_source-web_00700.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240509_FI_source-web_00700.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：騰訊官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">將於今日派成績表的阿里巴巴(09988)與網易(09999)，今早於競價時段同樣向好；阿里巴巴開報131.4元，升0.77%；網易開報169.8元，升2.23%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">同樣在今日公布業績的尚有吉利汽車(00175)，該股今早開報19.16元，升0.1%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14930140-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e9%9d%a0%e7%a9%a9-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%be%ae%e5%8d%873%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b123644%e9%bb%9e",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-15 09:26:35",
